    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Districts within a city, town, or other community marked out for specific governmental or administrative purposes, such as for electoral, school, or police services.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
